gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Spurs 130, Pistons 108
gameRecap.excerpt: The Spurs defeated the Pistons, 130-108 and move to 6-30 on the year. Victor Wembanyama led the Spurs with his first career triple-double, totaling 16 points, 12 rebounds, 10 assists, and 0 turnovers as Keldon Johnson added 17 points. Jalen Duren led the Pistons with 21 points and 12 rebounds. The Pistons move to 3-35.
